  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the underground, then again, came with all kind of coupons because she had to buy food and clothing and all this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, you know, you needed coupons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the underground, of course, did enough break-ins in the, you know, in the German buildings where they got hold of the stamps, and all this, food stamps.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, well, I was told when I was there that if I, anybody asked that I had to say I came from the bombed-out city of Ram-- Rotterdam.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rotterdam at the beginning of the war was really bombed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, a lot of kids had to-- were moved out because, you know, it was not rebuilt at all.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had to tell them that, you know, I was from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
